# Mintlify automatically ignores these files and directories:
# .git, .github, .claude, .agents, .idea, node_modules,
# README.md, LICENSE.md, CHANGELOG.md, CONTRIBUTING.md

# Draft content
drafts/
*.draft.mdx

# Planning material — kept in repo for contributors but not published
docs-plan/

# Version archive folders — empty until M3 cuts. v2026.05.11/ is the first
# archive (cut in DEV-1909/1910/1912). Future EMPTY future archive folders
# (e.g., v2026.05.20/) still need ignoring until they're populated, but the
# specific pattern would go here per-cutover rather than blanket-ignoring all
# of them. For now nothing future is staged, so no pattern needed.
